Set of Groovy scripts supporting Java development. Please check the original post at

http://blog.novoj.net/2011/06/15/groovy-namisto-shell-skriptu/

Steps necessary to run this script:

1) install Groovy (http://groovy.codehaus.org)
2) [OPTIONAL BUT RECOMMENDED] install GroovyServ (http://kobo.github.com/groovyserv)
3) create new GSCRIPT_HOME variable pointing to gscript
4) add gscript to your PATH environment variable
5) run "gscript"